{"tid":1304650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家其實係咪唔記得咗兄弟爬山,各有各做呢句嘢?","createTime":"2019-07-10T16:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T16:34:20.000Z","uid":245988,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3e1800a19a99f8dc751d380468f23053772b44","tid":1304650,"uid":245988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:10:01.000Z","msg":"見到宜家好多post都喺度緊連儂牆嘅可行性,抵制CCTVB嘅事,令到我覺得連登開始出現意見嘅對立.(意見和而不同係好事)<br />\n所以我希望大家緊記:<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山,各有各做</span></span><br />\n就等覺得連儂牆有用的人繼續做佢哋認為覺得有用嘅嘢;覺得呢種方法成效一般嘅人希望你哋至少抱持著一種不反對嘅態度,同時提出令成件事更加好嘅方法,例如memo盡量focus返喺五大訴求,盡量少啲帶有仇恨情緒嘅memo等等,<br />\n<br />\n始終大家都是想件事好,冷靜啲商量,理性啲傾,無壞嘅.<br />\n<br />\nP.S. Sorry for 1999,以上純屬個人睇法,歡迎各位討論!<br />\n希望大家可以繼續專注於抗爭嘅工作,香港人加油,自己香港自己救."},{"pid":"31184eeca32b74da1f53f576c336a690e87d89e5","tid":1304650,"uid":15129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cae82c63994a14180e5e9f7a8c66fd8c25186068","tid":1304650,"uid":226560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6yBC01W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yBC01W.png&h=dbfe3f5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06322d239b2cf7f6eb09ee6218f5e019a3b45738","tid":1304650,"uid":263423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cf529bcb7c0a1fe08e38c7d8128d32e5c2c371","tid":1304650,"uid":259515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"08fbbe4766ee35e18dbad2806308a543b8df12ff","tid":1304650,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im